  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个DMA控制器的状态机图。整体流程是从IDLE开始，收到Kick-off信号后进入FETCH取指，解析完成后根据有效性分支到ARB_READ或者ERROR。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "Kick-off",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。仲裁之后呢？ARB_READ到READ之间应该有个授权信号吧？另外WRITE之后是直接进入完成状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "WRITE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ARB_READ收到Grant后进入READ，读完成进入ARB_WRITE，再Grant到WRITE。写完之后有个关键点——我们要支持链式传输，所以WRITE完成后先到CHAIN状态，由CHAIN判断是继续FETCH下一块还是结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE",
        "Grant",
        "Complete",
        "Next",
        "Last"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把CHAIN画出来了，分支到FETCH和COMPLETE。那COMPLETE之后呢？还有ERROR状态怎么恢复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "COMPLETE之后发中断回到IDLE，标记为IRQ sent。ERROR需要软件清除，也是回到IDLE，标记SW clear。另外初始状态从[*]指向IDLE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "IDLE",
        "ERROR",
        "IRQ sent",
        "SW clear",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：PARSE到ARB_READ的条件是Valid，到ERROR是Invalid。FETCH到PARSE是Complete，READ到ARB_WRITE也是Complete，WRITE到CHAIN也是Complete——这几个Complete会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "Valid",
        "Invalid",
        "FETCH",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不会，它们发生在不同阶段，标注一样的文字没问题。视觉上可以用不同层级的颜色区分，比如主状态用浅绿色背景，仲裁状态用灰色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "primaryColor",
        "secondaryColor",
        "e8f4e8",
        "f5f5f5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经按v2语法画好了，用了base主题，主状态填了#e8f4e8，边框用深绿色。所有转移标签都核对过了，从初始状态到IDLE，CHAIN的Next/Last分支，以及两条回到IDLE的路径都完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
